title: Championship weekend's biggest potential winners/losers; Game breakdowns and picks; Gase/Williams Jets marriage; Clemson/White House overreaction
itunes:title: Championship weekend's biggest potential winners/losers; Game breakdowns and picks; Gase/Williams Jets marriage; Clemson/White House overreaction
description:
Subscribe here to the 3 and Out with John Middlekauff Podcast https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/3-and-out-with-john-middlekauff/id1352730623?mt=2.  Middlekauff looks at Championship Weekend's biggest potential winners and losers, his game breakdowns and picks, why he's bullish on the Adam Gase and Gregg Williams marriage with the Jets, why the Cowboys won't win a Super Bowl with Jason Garrett, social media pearl clutching over Clemson's White House fast food dinner, and answers listener questions in Middlekauff's Mailbag.
